{"tid":783671,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新股】傳海底撈集資10億美元 下周上市聆訊","createTime":"2018-08-17T16:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T01:58:38.000Z","uid":171681,"like":4,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"877c6ddab05d11fcfe6d0bbe5f87a8aa8906ff24","tid":783671,"uid":171681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T16:55:12.000Z","msg":"外電引述消息人士稱，海底撈計劃來港上市，擬集資最多10億美元，並於下周四（23日）進行上市聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n內媒則報道指，海底撈上市定價區間90億至120億美元，按照2019年預計淨利潤計算，相當於22至28倍市盈率。基礎投資者的角逐已進入最後階段，將選擇一家國際長線基金、一家主權基金和一家大型中資基金成為基石投資者，目前最有可能勝出的是貝萊德、中投和高領資本。<br />\n<br />\n早前，消息指海底撈初步計劃於9月10日來港上市，並早於五月份遞交上市申請，據公司初步上市文件顯示，公司去年錄得盈利10.28億元人民幣，按年增長4成。<br />\n<br />\n同系的頤海國際（1579）偏軟，收市報14.38元，跌2.04%，成交7,536萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180815&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58566562\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180815%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58566562&d=ZNJE44%2FX61GjFTrrixCz7HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=95f116b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180815%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58566562&h=6622f408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180815&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58566562</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baf91fc02371b71304becd63e72ebf4a45a4e04b","tid":783671,"uid":11895,"like":52,"dislike":4,"score":48,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:00:20.000Z","msg":"一間19餐廳值90億美金<br />\n戇撚尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ed8d7f3163ff669eb53f777b627f76e1e54354","tid":783671,"uid":17176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"唔撚掂 仲鳩過中國屎塔"},{"pid":"a6e960d56c7ee24e5e306946da65d1f1e284630c","tid":783671,"uid":71748,"lik